Harden your installation
##########################

There is one security risk based on the fact, that it is required to store
the ebay password(s) during making a bid in plain text in file system.

This esniper configuration file will removed automaticly abt. 15 sec after
esniper start.


Secure access
###############

To generally secure your installation, you can install on a host only
accessible by https.


Restrict access
#################

Restrict general access to valid users with .htaccess / .htpasswd
You can use for this the provided access.php which uses a modified
phpAccess.php with user->esfadmin, password->adminpassword

Change access.php to your needs.
